title: Serious team looking for supp, Plat 3+
body:
Looking for a support Plat 3+ to play with before the next season kicks off. Our current 5's team is Plat 1 but will probably start up new team with the new line up we have an adjust to the meta before playing on the main team again. 

Add me if you're interested IGN: aSlayer. 

Thanks

Skype required.
